name: Powered up! (Babylord23)
description:
An incremental game I made. Next update will release on a Saturday. Not saying which one.

Click and drag power cells into the box to get power. Buy upgrades and continue from there.
You unlock stuff at: 5 power: settings/upgrades

10000 total power: reset layer 1

1mil reset layer 1 currency (no spoilers!) :  reset layer 2

no further content yet, but feel free to upgrade and get bigger number!
